text: Abdelmalek Ali Messaoud (27 May 1955 – 6 February 2022وفاة اللاعب الدولي السابق لكرة القدم عبد المالك علي مسعود ) was an Algerian football player and manager. He played as a defender for USM Alger.Abdelmalek Ali Messaoud - عبد المالك علي مسعود ; DZFootball.free.fr He had 38 appearances and one goal for the Algeria national team between 1974 until 1978. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Algerian footballers
title: Abdelmalek Ali Messaoud
